          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-gold/10 border border-gold/30 rounded-lg">
          <p class="text-text-primary font-medium text-sm mb-1">If you're in crisis</p>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
            National Suicide Prevention Lifeline: <strong>988</strong> | Crisis Text Line: Text <strong>HOME</strong> to <strong>741741</strong>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
